title: Bull market is still in the 6th inning, says Sandip Bhagat
text:
Bull market is still in the 6th inning, says Sandip Bhagat 2:59pm EDT - 05:54
Whittier Trust's CIO tells Reuters' Fred Katayama that with no signs of a recession, stocks can extend their rally a few more years. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
